OL,3,CCalls for care home 'top up fees'
OL,4,Creform
OL,6,FFOIs sent to all of Northern Ireland's
OL,7,Fhealth trusts show that the spectrum
OL,8,Fof top fees ranges from #6.50 to over
OL,9,F#500 a week. They also show that the
OL,10,Fmajority of the independent care
OL,11,Fproviders who run over 80% of care
OL,12,Fhomes in Northern Ireland charge such
OL,13,Ffees. It's a massive financial
OL,14,Fcommitment for any one and one which
OL,15,Ffamilies tell UTV, is a process which
OL,16,Fis difficult to navigate.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/16
