OL,3,CCalls for care home 'top up fees'
OL,4,Creform
OL,6,FAge NI told UTV that the system needs
OL,7,Fto be made much clearer and easier for
OL,8,Findividuals to use. Brenda Kearns, Age
OL,9,FNI, told UTV that there are cases
OL,10,Fwhere people are paying top up fees
OL,11,Fwho shouldn't be paying out. Brenda
OL,12,Fsays that if the health trust only
OL,13,Foffers one viable residential or
OL,14,Fnursing home option, then technically
OL,15,Fpeople shouldn't have to pay the fee
OL,16,Fat all.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/16
