OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F443A1755721478
OL,3,CCalls for care home 'top up fees'
OL,4,Creform
OL,6,FBrenda Kearns from Age NI agrees. She
OL,7,Fsays they regularly deal with people
OL,8,Fwho have signed a contract to pay
OL,9,Fthese fees, often during moments of
OL,10,Femotional turmoil as they take the
OL,11,Fdifficult decision to put their
OL,12,Frelative into care, but don't realise
OL,13,Fthat those fees can rise. She says
OL,14,Fthis has caused an influx of people,
OL,15,Foften desperately worried, coming to
OL,16,Fthe organisation looking for
OL,17,Fassistance. Some she says should never
OL,18,Fhave been paying these fees in the
OL,19,Ffirst place.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/16
