OL,4,Creform
OL,6,FThe Department of Heath is in
OL,7,Fagreement about the need for reform.
OL,8,FIt told UTV that fundamental reform of
OL,9,Fthe social care sector is needed to
OL,10,Fbuild a more sustainable, equitable
OL,11,Fand resilient sector that better
OL,12,Fserves the population of Northern
OL,13,FIreland.
OL,15,FThis reform is being taken forward by
OL,16,Fthe Social Care Collaborative Forum
OL,17,F(SCCF).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/16
