OL,3,CCalls for care home 'top up fees'
OL,4,Creform
OL,6,FA key objective of the Commissioning
OL,7,Fand Contracting Workstream of the SCCF
OL,8,Fis to review and update the current
OL,9,Fregional residential and nursing home
OL,10,Fspecification and contract. This work,
OL,11,Fwhich includes reviewing existing
OL,12,Ffinance issues across the care home
OL,13,Fsector including the regional care
OL,14,Fhome tariff and third-party
OL,15,Fcontributions, is at an advanced stage.
OL,17,FThe Southern and Western Health trusts
OL,18,Falso provided statements to UTV.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/16
