OL,4,Creform
OL,6,FThe Southern Trust said that top-up
OL,7,Ffees are charged when there is a
OL,8,Fdifference being charged by the
OL,9,Findividual care home which has been
OL,10,Fchosen by the resident or their family
OL,11,Fand the rate which the trust would
OL,12,Fnormally expect to pay to meet the
OL,13,Fcare needs of that resident.
OL,15,F"The Trust does not charge a Top up on
OL,16,Fits Trust owned beds."
