OL,6,FThe Western Trust says that HSC Trusts
OL,7,Fhave a responsibility to secure best
OL,8,Fvalue for money and protect the public
OL,9,Ffunds for which they are accountable.
OL,10,FThird Party Contributions are managed
OL,11,Fin line with the Circular HSC (ECCU) 1/
OL,12,F2010 Care Management, Provision of
OL,13,FServices and Charging Guidance and
OL,14,FCharging for Residential Accommodation
OL,15,FGuide.
