OL,6,FIt says that when information is
OL,7,Fpresented to the Trust that requires a
OL,8,Freview the Trust will undertake this
OL,9,Freview taking into account all the
OL,10,Finformation available as per the
OL,11,FCircular detailed above.
OL,13,FIt reiterates that Independent
OL,14,Fproviders of Residential and Nursing
OL,15,FHome Care determine their own charge
OL,16,Ffor the bed which may or may not be
OL,17,Fabove the regionally agreed rate.
