OL,4,Creform
OL,6,FThese fees can be paid via the Trust
OL,7,For directly by the Third Party to the
OL,8,Fprovider in line the Circular HSC
OL,9,F(ECCU) 1/2010 Care Management,
OL,10,FProvision of Services and Charging
OL,11,FGuidance.
OL,13,FWhen asked about the issue of top-up
OL,14,Ffees the Independent Health and Care
OL,15,FProviders body which represents
OL,16,Findependent care providers told UTV
OL,17,Fthat it understands why people are
OL,18,Fconfused by the complexity around care
OL,19,Fhome fees.
