OL,6,FIt adds that in the interests of
OL,7,Ftransparency, it has been asking the
OL,8,FDepartment of Health to carry out an
OL,9,Findependent economic review of the
OL,10,Ftrue cost of care. It states that this
OL,11,Fwork is critical to inform an open,
OL,12,Fclear, and fair care home fee
OL,13,Fstructure and to determine who pays
OL,14,Ffor what.
