OL,6,FIt says that the Department has
OL,7,Faccepted that the review is necessary
OL,8,Fbut over the years there have been
OL,9,Fnumerous delays. It says that it is in
OL,10,Ffrequent communication with the
OL,11,FDepartment of Health pressing for this
OL,12,Fwork to commence urgently.
OL,14,FMichael and Margaret say they are
OL,15,Fspeaking out to emphasise the need for
OL,16,Freform of this complicated system...as
OL,17,Ffamilies across Northern Ireland
OL,18,Fstruggle with these costs.
